    "name": "Backrooms 清洁小队 (Backrooms Cleanup Crew)",
    "steam_appid": 3140990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Backrooms Cleanup Crew</strong>是一款多人清洁模拟器，玩家将扮演F-Corp公司的一名普通清洁员。你需要清理其他公司在“后室”（Backrooms）中制造的混乱。然而，在后室中，事情从来没有那么简单：尽可能快速地清理每个房间，同时躲避越来越致命的入侵事件。<br><br><strong>Backrooms Cleanup Crew</strong>目前包含14个可玩关卡，体验全部独特内容平均需要3小时。在抢先体验期间，我们将陆续添加更多关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/57006ab041222142dbf7a285147a1b46.poster.avif?t=1760976123\" width=1000 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/57006ab041222142dbf7a285147a1b46.webm?t=1760976123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/57006ab041222142dbf7a285147a1b46.mp4?t=1760976123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与最多三位玩家组队，快速完成各种关卡的清理任务。根据不同的清洁需求切换喷嘴类型，优化清理效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/2135c0699d32f4a9faf73253393329ef.poster.avif?t=1760976123\" width=1000 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/2135c0699d32f4a9faf73253393329ef.webm?t=1760976123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/2135c0699d32f4a9faf73253393329ef.mp4?t=1760976123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了擦洗墙壁，你还需要收集并清理关卡中的所有物品。不用担心太小心翼翼——可以随意将物品扔到房间里以加快进度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/b5fb930796b996c9eaf6b3a4cafea973.poster.avif?t=1760976123\" width=1000 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/b5fb930796b996c9eaf6b3a4cafea973.webm?t=1760976123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/b5fb930796b996c9eaf6b3a4cafea973.mp4?t=1760976123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心愈加困难且致命的入侵事件——在躲避攻击的同时，清理发光的标记以阻止新的攻击生成。清除这些标记还能让你的清洁速度更快。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/b34b4b8b7f91188dc8974f95c330ab9e.poster.avif?t=1760976123\" width=1000 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/b34b4b8b7f91188dc8974f95c330ab9e.webm?t=1760976123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/b34b4b8b7f91188dc8974f95c330ab9e.mp4?t=1760976123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了上述的普通模式外，<strong>Backrooms Cleanup Crew</strong>还可以在困难和和平模式下进行游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/7cf21697fe047bcb4c4be6956043efbf.poster.avif?t=1760976123\" width=1000 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/7cf21697fe047bcb4c4be6956043efbf.webm?t=1760976123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/7cf21697fe047bcb4c4be6956043efbf.mp4?t=1760976123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Backrooms Cleanup Crew</strong>由一支两人团队开发，他们热爱多人合作游戏。我们非常感谢您的反馈，并期待通过您的支持让这款游戏变得更加有趣！</p>",
